ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 1}, {"Id": 1000239, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Writing letter to Imam is among the effected means and it has tremendous and surprising effects, because our master as it was narrated is strongly pitiful to his well-wishers. I have personally in several occasions written letter to him (peace be upon him) and I saw a tremendous and surprising effect. Write all that we shall mention and drop it in any of the tomb of the Imams (peace be on them) or you wrap it and cover it with pure soil and drop it there, or you throw it into a river or deep well or into a pond of water, surely it shall reach the leader of the time peace be on him, he shall personally take control of your demands.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Tawassul aur isteghaase ki qismo’n mein Hazrat Baqiyyatullah Mawlana Saahebaz Zamaan (a) ki khidmat mein Ariza likhna hai is amal ki taaseer hairat-angez hai. Hamare Sayyad o Sardaar apne chahne waalo’n ke saath bohot ziyadah mohabbat o shafqat se pesh aate hai, jaisa keh riwaayat mein waarid huwa hai, ham ne kai baar Aan Hazrat (a) ki khidmat mein ariza likha aur uske hairat-angez aasaar mushaaheda kiye hai. Is maqaam par mukhtalif ariza jo Imam ki khidnat mein likhe jaate hai us se mutalliq baaz haqaayate’n jo buzurgo’n se mansoob hai naql karenge. Kitaab Tohfatur Razaviya mein tehreer hai, Allama-e-buzurg Jaleel-ul-qadr Sayed Mohammad Taqi Isfahani Hazrat Baqiyyatullah arwa-hona fidah ke mojizaat mein farmate hai; Hazrat keh roshan aur nooraani mojizaat aur unki aash-kaar karaamate yeh hai keh Hazrat (a) ki khidmat mein ariza bhejne se haajate’n poori aur maqsad hal hote hai, is amr ka aankho’n se mushaaheda kiya gaya hai aur vijdaan ne tajurba kiya hai. Allama Shaikh Abdul Husain Ameeni saahab kitaab Al-Ghadeer ne is se mutalliq ek hairat-angez hakaayat ham se naql ki: woh Hazrat se mutawassil hone aur uske baad jo waaqeya uske saath pesh aaya usey ham se naql farmaya, al-batta unho ne is kitaab mein usey bayaan karne ki ijaazat nahi farmayi thi, unho ne Aan Hazrat (a) ki khidmat mein Ariza likha aur Aan Hazxrat (a) se mutawassil huwe, unka bayaan hai; mai mohim (ahem) umoor mein apna maqsad haasil karne ke liye Hazrat se tawassul ka tajurba kiya hai.", "UrduDescription": "کچھ واقعات کو حضرت کے عریضہ کے فوائد کے بارے میں بیان کیا اب یہ بتارہاہوں کہ عریضہ کس طرح لکھیں ایک عبارت کاغذ پر لکھ کر ائمہ معصومین میں سے کسی ایک کی ضریح میں ڈال دیں یہ عریضہ حضرت حجت کی خدمت میں پہنچ جاتاہے اور خود حضرت اس کی حاجت کو پوری کرتے ہیں اور کاغذ پر اس طرح لکھیں۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": 