ull, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000240, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I have written to you O my master, may His mercy and blessing be on you, seeking a favour from you. I have complained to you for what has happened to me seeking solutions firstly from Allah and then from you for a matter that has obsessed me.I am helpless in combating the problem and for that I have resorted to seeking help from Allah and from you. Knowing the status you have with Allah. I am confident that you will help me get the solutions to my problems swiftly and that you will intercede on my behalf. I am helpless and moreover I am sinful:So help O master and present this problem to Allah and I pray to Him that He will solve this quickly and grant me victory and success in finding the solution to my problems.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Baadshah'e jinn o ins, Imam'e waqt Hujjatul Qa’em ibne Imam Hazrat Hasan Askari (a.s) laakho’n durrood o salaam ho aap par, aap ke jadd'e amjad par aur aap ki aulaad'e tahera par, aap ki zaat mohtaj'e bayaan nahin, aap jaante hai keh mai kis mushkil mein giraftaar hu, is museebat se Siwaaye Khuda aur aap ki zaat ke kisi ko apna madadgaar nahi chahta hu, aur apni pareshani o museebato’n aur duaawo ki fariyaad lekar aap ke darbaar mein aaya hu, aur is arize ke zariye aap ki bargah mein isteghasa karta hu, aur umeed-waar hu keh Panjetan'e paak ke sadqe se aur Allah (s.w.t) ke naam par aap ghaib se meri mushkilo’n ko aasaan kar do. Mai aap ko waasta deta hu aap ke jadd'e amjad ka sar'e sighafta Ali'e Murtaza (a.s) ka, pehlu'e shikasta Janaab'e Sayyeda (s.a) ka, Janab'e Hassan'e Mujtaba (a.s) ka, khoon'e Hussein (a.s) ka, be-rida Zainab o Kulsoom (s.a) ka aur Sakina (s.a) ke niyle rukhsaar ka. “Ya to khwaab mein mujhe is pareshani ka haal bataawo’n, ya ghaib se hamari mushkil ko aasaan kar do”. Mujhe umeed hai ke aap mujhe khaali haath nahi pherenge, aur mera sawaal ko apni sakhi bargah mein bohot jald pura farmaayenge. Mai Gunah-gaar hu meri arz yeh hai keh…", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "کَتَبْتُ اِلَیْكَ یَا مَوْلَایَ صَلَوَاتُ اللہِ عَلَیْکَ مُسْتَغِیْثًا، وَشَکَوْتُ مَا نَزَلَ بِیْ مُسْتَجِیْرًا بِاللہِ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ، ثُمَّ بِکَ مِنْ اَمْرٍ قَدْ دَھَمَنِیْ، وَاَشْغَلَ قَلْبِیْ، وَاَطَالَ فِکْرِیْ، وَسَلَبَنِیْ بَعْضَ لُبِّیْ، وَغَیْرَ خَطِیْرِ نِعْمَۃِ اللہِ عِنْدِیْ، اَسْلَمَنِیْ عِنْدَ تَخَیُّلِ وُرُوْدِہِ الْخَلِیْلُ، وَتَبَرَّاَ مِنِّیْ عِنْدَ تَرَآئِیْ اِقْبَالِہٖ اِلَیَّ الْحَمِیْمِ، وَعَجَزَتْ عَنْ دِفَاعِہٖ حِیْلَتِیْ، وَخَانَنِیْ فِیْ تَحَمُّلِہٖ صَبْرِیْ وَقَوَّتِیْ۔ فَلْجَاْتُ فِیْہِ اِلَیْکَ، وَتَوَ کَّلْتُ فِیْ الْمَسْأَلَۃِ لِلہِ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ ثَنَاؤُہٗ عَلَیْہِ وَعَلَیْکَ وَفِیْ دِفَاعِہٖ عَنِّیْ، عِلْمًۢا بِمَکَانِکَ مِنَ اللہِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ، وَلِیِّ التَّدْبِیْرِ وَمَالِکِ الْاُمُوْرِ، وَاثِقًا بِکَ فِیْ الْمُسَارَعَۃِ فِیْ الشَّفَاعَۃِ اِلَیْہِ جَلَّ ثَنَاؤُہٗ فِیْ اَمْرِیْ، مُتَیَقِّنًا لِاِجَابَتِہٖ تَبَارَکَ وَ تَعَالٰی اِیَّاکَ بِاِعْطَائِیْ سُؤْلِیْ۔ وَاَنْتَ یَامَوْلَایَ جَدِیْرٌۢ بِتَحْقِیْقِ ظَنِّیْ وَتَصْدِیْقِ اَمَلِیْ فِیْکَ فِیْ اَمْرٍ کَذَا وَ کَذَا۔۔۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": nul